  "texts": [
    "This use of text as the latent representation of an image may provide a promising avenue of research.",
    "Final notesVision-Language tasks such as image captioning and VQA pose significant opportunities for accessibility technology to be developed for those with sight impairment or severe sight impairment.",
    "Having widespread automatic alt-text generation on websites and applications enabling queries about images shared online, there is substantial impact that research in these fields can have.",
    "However, models trained on current datasets are prone to the biases of sighted humans.",
    "The questions asked in VQA datasets, and the captions given in image captioning datasets do not necessarily cater to the needs of possible end users of this technology."
